{"tid":2197263,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（警世）想戒煙。。","createTime":"2020-09-10T13:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T03:20:40.000Z","uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d81d33314c8e3cfc4a1fa60db1fb0f9e66dd42e","tid":2197263,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T13:01:44.000Z","msg":"本身份工好大壓力。。一日至少食半包。。女朋友發現左之後想我戒 跟住就試下唔食 點知唔食真係好難頂 又冇精神 個人又攰 啲戒癮症狀出哂黎。。<br />\n<br />\n聽人講食電子煙冇咁大癮 可以轉食 再慢慢戒甩<br />\n<br />\n但食左之後係食少左 同冇咁大癮 但始終發覺都係戒唔甩 一大壓力既時候就想放空個人 繼而就會再食。。<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位成功戒到煙既Ching重有咩方法戒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ab9f3654cc8e6bf031c8dc9f7274db11e8cf80","tid":2197263,"uid":348747,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T13:03:10.000Z","msg":"vape cbd oil"},{"pid":"01bef7da6435504435b2126228ebd2df618856c5","tid":2197263,"uid":65638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T13:04:34.000Z","msg":"我係用飲水戒煙<br />\n一想食煙就飲水<br />\n12 歲開始食左10幾年都戒倒"},{"pid":"77155dd833035a387cc6aa5a89d53d7da7710803","tid":2197263,"uid":2300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"唔好戒啦 食多d&hellip;<br />\n食到好地地做咩要戒！？ 見字快d食多支"},{"pid":"2da05c25801fd5b8dd9856500e3b1b4d1f8b073a","tid":2197263,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77155dd833035a387cc6aa5a89d53d7da7710803","tid":2197263,"uid":2300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"唔好戒啦 食多d&hellip;<br />\n食到好地地做咩要戒！？ 見字快d食多支"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/142123_1d21315d52ad51c69de2b92e99800201.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F142123_1d21315d52ad51c69de2b92e99800201.gif&h=57a1d649&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70420bee4811c9b31f5e5ebbb24d4985a2567d58","tid":2197263,"uid":64992,"like":0,"disl